node.text: Gotta brush up on your Terry Silver? Here are 5 must-know facts about the diabolical villain from Daniel’s past.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cobra Kai on May 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1 FOUNDER COBRA ΚΑΙ IN THE KARATE KID PART 3, WE LEARN THAT JOHN KREESE CREATED COBRA ΚΑΙ WITH TERRY SILVER-HIS SILVER OLD WAR BUDDY WHOSE NICKNAME WAS "TWIG."'.

Photo by Cobra Kai on May 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2 MONEY MONEY MONEY: WHEN NOT TRAINING IN COBRA ΚΑΙ. TERRY SILVER'S DAY JOB WAS RUNNING DYNATOX, A TOXIC WASTE DISPOSAL COMPANY THAT MADE HIM ONE OF THE RICHEST MEN IN THE VALLEY.'.

Photo by Cobra Kai on May 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3 DANIEL'S ECOND SENSEI: IN THE KARATE KID PART 3, TERRY SILVER MANIPULATES DANIEL INTO JOINING COBRA ΚΑΙ. CREATING A RIFT BETWEEN DANIEL AND MR. MIYAGI.'.

Photo by Cobra Kai on May 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4 THE FINER THINGS: TERRY SILVER HAS IMPECCABLE TASTE, FROM HIGH END CARS,TO TO GOLDEN TELEPHONES, PRIVATE STEAM ROOMS, DESIGNER CLOTHES, ASCOTS ETC.'.
Photo by Cobra Kai on May 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 PONYTAIL: TERRY SILVER HAS LONG HAIR AND TIES IT IN A PONYTAIL, SO HIS HAIR DOESN'T GET IN HIS FACE WHEN HE ATTACKS YOU.'.
